# Ubuntu
1. mkdir deb
2. bump verion in DEBIAN/control
3. copy DEBIAN directory into deb
4. create docs dir: deb/usr/share/doc/pianobar-version/
5. create binary dir deb/usr/bin/
6. compile and copy pianobar executable into deb/usr/bin/
7. gzip COPYING and README into docs dir
8. copy contrib into docs dir
9. dpkg -b ./deb pianobar-version-i386.deb
